      <title>亚马逊取消美国杂货店的无收银系统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/amazon-pulls-plug-on-cashierless-system-in-us-grocery-stores</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚马逊公司(Amazon.com Inc.)正在从杂货店中移除其无收银员Just Walk Out系统，这是一项旨在让购物者免排队的雄心勃勃的技术的撤退。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/amazon-pulls-plug-on-cashierless-system-in-us-grocery-stores</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 15:46:40 GMT</pubDate>
